        <div class="page-header text-center">
            <h1>Use what you have!</h1>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center  copy">
            So much of our culture is based around either eating out of the house, or buying on a whim without considering what is already in the house. With "Waste Not" you can use what you have to find recipes you can make. No more waste. The recipes shown to you are tailored to your taste and diet if need be. Of course, one's fridge sometimes isn't enough to make a full meal, that's why you can make the missing ingredients directly delivered to you via BringMeister with your PayPal account.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

